stock = "USIM5"

StockData = CorrectedData.loc[CorrectedData["CODNEG"]==stock].copy() #dados do ativo subjacente (VALE3)

StockData["relHLOC"] = ((StockData["PREULT"]-StockData["PREABE"])/(StockData["PREMAX"]-StockData["PREMIN"]))

StockData["OC"] = (StockData["PREULT"]/StockData["PREABE"])
StockData["HL"] = (StockData["PREMAX"]/StockData["PREMIN"])

maxOC = (StockData["PREULT"].combine(StockData["PREABE"],max,0))
minOC = (StockData["PREULT"].combine(StockData["PREABE"],min,0))

StockData["relMax"] = ((StockData["PREMAX"]-maxOC)/(StockData["PREMAX"]-StockData["PREMIN"]))
StockData["relMin"] = ((minOC-StockData["PREMIN"])/(StockData["PREMAX"]-StockData["PREMIN"]))

#StockData["VolRel"] = (StockData["VOLTOT"]/StockData["VOLTOT"].mean())


Headers = ["relHLOC","OC","HL","relMax","relMin"]#, "VolRel"]
p = [10 for i in range(0,len(Headers))]

ARHeaders = []

for i,h in enumerate(Headers):
    for p_i in range(0,p[i]):
        StockData[f"{h}_{p_i}"] = StockData[h].shift(p_i)
        ARHeaders.append(f"{h}_{p_i}")

StockData["retorno_af"] = StockData["PREULT"].pct_change(max(p)).shift(-max(p)).ewm(span=5).mean()+1

data2reg = StockData[ARHeaders + ["retorno_af"]].dropna()

n = data2reg.shape[0]//3
x_train, x_test = data2reg[ARHeaders].iloc[:n], data2reg[ARHeaders].iloc[n:]
y_train, y_test = data2reg["retorno_af"].iloc[:n], data2reg["retorno_af"].iloc[n:]

X = x_train
y = y_train

A = X.T@X
b = X.T@y

theta = np.linalg.solve(A,b)

end = data2reg.index.to_pydatetime()[-1]

start = end-timedelta(days=365*5+1)


StockDataMT5 = anl.MQLDataGet(stock,start,end)
In[121]:
fig,axs = plt.subplots(2,1,figsize=(20,10))

y_pred = (data2reg[ARHeaders]@theta.T)

y_pred.plot(ax=axs[0])
data2reg["retorno_af"].plot(ax=axs[1])

updown_pred = (y_pred.apply(np.log)/y_pred.apply(np.log).abs())
updown_true = (data2reg["retorno_af"].apply(np.log)/data2reg["retorno_af"].apply(np.log).abs())

print("acuracia: " + str((updown_pred == updown_true).sum()/updown_true.shape[0]))


axs[0].set_title("Sinal Predito")
axs[1].set_title("Sinal Original Filtrado")

plt.tight_layout(pad=1.11)

CAPEX = 5000
tx = 0
imposto = 1-0.2 #20% -> 80% de lucro


signal = updown_pred.rolling(7).median().fillna(0)

K = (signal.shift().fillna(signal.iloc[0]) != signal)*tx/CAPEX


fig,axs = plt.subplots(2,1,figsize=(20,10))

(imposto*signal.shift()*StockData["PREABE"].pct_change().fillna(0)+1-K).cumprod().plot(ax=axs[0])
(StockData["PREABE"].pct_change()+1).cumprod().plot(ax=axs[0])

signal.plot(figsize=(20,10),ax =axs[1])

axs[1].set_title("Long/Short signal")

plt.tight_layout(pad=1.11)
